text: Fox News Guest gets called out for CLAIMING he's from 'Chicago' (really from the burbs!) posted by Erik Zachary - share About me The spark notes version? I'm an avid Starbucks People Watcher and Professional Wingman who spends every day just trying to make 'em laugh (Singing in the Rain reference). Want more? I was born and raised in a small suburb northwest of Chicago (Bartlett). I'm the type of guy who breaks the awkward silence in an elevator just to make it more awkward and I LOVE music. I'm dancing or making weird sounds 98% of the time, live FIRMLY by the idea of living each and every moment as if it's your last....OH and I'm currently learning to fly a plane, so....ya know...might be a good idea to keep your head up and watch out.Keep in touch!
